{
  "stem": "4700.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the parishioners complained to the authorities they can't get to the church because of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] About a year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had secret sort of-- they called it circles-- about six, seven Jewish children went to a private home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to always go piecemeal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't ever go together, because that-- it was forbidden to teach Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people who were university students or perhaps professional teachers came and taught us various subjects.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I did that for a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we sort of were allowed to take external exams at the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then after-- the next year, after the transport started, the whole thing was in a state of flux.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because people sort of were taken into transports all the time, and you couldn't maintain it properly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, people didn't have much money anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so the whole thing just petered out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finished-- I think, I'm not sure whether I finished third or fourth-year high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought I finished fourth-year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't find the examination results, so perhaps I only finished [LAUGHS] third-year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think, I think it was fourth-year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did a course in, in graphics.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always liked drawing, so I did a course in graphics and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sort of craft and various other things, which you thought might be useful.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six and a half, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "11 And a half.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I went two years to high school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, district high school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was only the elementary school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you see, in-- in Czechoslovakia, there were two grades of high school-- the academic high school, the gymnasium, as they called it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
